detaileddescription.para:
Asynchronously queries the numbers of streamers connected to the signalling server.
OnNumStreamersReceived
Callback fired when the query for the number of streamers returns.

A native C++ implementation of a Pixel Streaming signalling server (similar to cirrus.js). This implementation is missing some features such as SFU and Webserver support. The purpose of this implementation is to have signalling server callable from UE, without bundling Cirrus itself.
